http://www.execreport.com:80/zine/0595.Update.2.html 192.204.56.67 19970115133901 text/html 21666
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 13:44:06 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4.1
