<DOCNO>WT10-B35-70</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000345-B037-141</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.execreport.com:80/zine/0495.Supplement.html 192.204.56.67 19970115134517 text/html 21392
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 13:50:24 GMT
