<p>
<b><FONT SIZE=+2> Golf Course Guide: </FONT></B><br><FONT SIZE=+1><b>Here's everything you ever wanted to know about the golf courses in Allegheny County but didn't have time to research yourself.</FONT SIZE></b><br>
<i>By ER Staff</i>
<hr>
Executive Report is pleased to bring you a directory of nearly 50 golf courses in Allegheny County. The information was researched and compiled by free-lancer Don Rebel. In the guide, we list the information you need to know to easily plan a round for yourself or for friends and clients. <P> The courses are arranged alphabetically and are categorized as public, private or semi-private. We wanted the guide to be as complete as possible, however, some courses did not supply all the requested information. As always, we welcome your comments.
<HR>
<font size =+2><B>Public Courses: </B></font size> <BR>
