<HR>
<!img align=left src="../pictures/0295.Supplement.1.gif"><FONT SIZE=+2><B>Education Guide: </FONT SIZE></B>
<FONT SIZE=+1><b>Guide To Southwestern Pennsylvania Colleges and Universities</FONT SIZE></b><br>
<i>By Kristin Giron</i>
<HR>
Executive Report is pleased to present this education guide, researched and compiled by Kristin Giron. Included in this alphabetically arranged listing are the colleges and universities in Allegheny, Armstrong, Beaver, Butler, Cambria, Fayette, Greene, Indiana, Lawrence, Somerset, Washington and Westmoreland counties.
<P>
The guide details admission criteria, academic departments and programs, financial aid information and special Nontraditional programs. In each case, upcoming academic programs are listed where available. Figures reflect the 1993-94 academic year. As always, your comments and suggestions are welcome.
<HR>
