 <HEAD>
  <TITLE>Write for Liberator</TITLE>
 </HEAD>
 <BODY BACKGROUND="backgrnd.jpg">
  <CENTER>
   <IMG SRC="border.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
   <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="scribe.gif">
   <H1>
    <IMG SRC="lib_on.gif"><BR><IMG SRC="wri_txt.gif" ALT="Writing For Liberator">
   </H1>
   <HR>
   <P>
    <STRONG><IMG SRC="name.gif" ALT="Liberator"> Publications,</STRONG><BR>
    Flat 1,<BR>
    24 Alexandra Grove,<BR>
    London,<BR>
    N4 2LF,<BR>
    E-mail: <A HREF="mailto:collective@liberator.org.uk">collective@liberator.org.uk</A>
   </P>
  </CENTER>
  <BR CLEAR=ALL>
  <P>Why not join the long list of MPs, Lords, Councillors and others who have written for <IMG SRC="name.gif" ALT="Liberator">?</P>
  <P><IMG SRC="name.gif" ALT="Liberator"> welcomes articles on any subject, up to 1500 words.</P>
  <P>If you don't want to submit articles by e-mail, we can accept your <IMG SRC="name.gif" ALT="Liberator"> contributions on floppy disk. We prefer MS-DOS format floppy disks (3.5" or 5.25" high or low density). Please send your file in WordPerfect 5.x, Microsoft Word or ASCII format.</P>
  <P>We reserve the right to shorten, alter or omit any material.</P>
