   <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="sub.gif">
   <H1>
    <IMG SRC="lib_on.gif"><BR><IMG SRC="sub_txt.gif" ALT="Subscriptions">
   </H1>
   <HR>
  </CENTER>
  <P>So you've seen the cool web pages, read the articles, wondered in astonishment at the group of hardened-drinkers and social misfits that make up the collective - and now it's time to subscribe.</P>
  <P>For just 14 you get eight issues, usually evenly-spaced throughout the year, although elections, court cases and general apathy can occasionally get in the way.</P>
  <P>And it's quite simple. All you have to do is fill in the form below and click 'subscribe'. We'll send you a form through the post as soon as possible.</P>
