<HTML>
  <HEAD>
    <TITLE>Liberator: Issue 234 Reviews</TITLE>
  </HEAD>
  <BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrnd.jpg">
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../read.gif">
      <H1><IMG SRC="../lib_on.gif"><BR>Issue 234 Reviews</H1>
      <BR CLEAR=ALL><HR>
      <H2>Leaving Las Vegas</H2>
      <H3>(Director Mike Figgis Cert 18)</H3>
    </CENTER>
    <P>This is a vehicle for the remarkable central performance of Nicolas Cage, who plays a self-confessed alcoholic who is about to deliberately slide down the slippery slope to oblivion. Selling all his assets and clearing his credit card bill he turns up in Las Vegas from Los Angeles determined to drink himself to death. Seeking companionship rather than sex he befriends a prostitute played by Elizabeth Shue who, in her own life, is in an habitually enslaved relationship with a pimp who has a vicious line in punishment involving scarring her legs with a knife when her takings are too low.</P>
    <P>But this subtext is not so much complementary but more a distraction to the main focus, which is an outstanding character study into the behaviour of an alcoholic with a death wish. Cage displays the tell tale behaviour of a  chronic alcoholic - the horror of early morning sobriety when the shakes in his hand prevent him from signing a cheque at the bank; the mild inebriation which allows him to engage in wry humour, the tell tale signs of drunkenness when he becomes accident prone leading to rage and violence, and finally the near comatose fits of a body suffering from acute alcohol poisoning.</P>
    <P>This is a modern tragedy with a believable anti-hero for which the audience can feel real sympathy. Not a fun film by any means, although there are some exceptionally funny episodes between the periods of dark despair, but essentially a great study of nihilistic values set against the back drop of the ultimate materialistic culture which is Las Vegas.</P>
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border2.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <A HREF="http://www.liberator.org.uk/cgi-bin/imagemap/imagemaps/buttons.map"><IMG SRC="../buttons.gif" BORDER=0 USEMAP="#BUTTONS" ISMAP></A>
      <map name="BUTTONS">
        <area shape="polygon" alt="Home Page" coords="32,2,4,23,1,56,85,56,81,25,56,22,33,2,33,3" href="http://www.liberator.org.uk/index.htm">
        <area shape="polygon" alt="The Collective" coords="88,40,91,59,138,59,144,47,118,1,101,0,96,39,89,39" href="http://www.liberator.org.uk/Collective/Collective.html">
