<HTML>
  <HEAD>
    <TITLE>Liberator: Issue 235 Reviews</TITLE>
  </HEAD>
  <BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrnd.jpg">
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../read.gif">
      <H1><IMG SRC="../lib_on.gif"><BR>Issue 235 Reviews</H1>
      <BR CLEAR=ALL><HR>
      <H2>Bongwater</H2>
      <H3>by Michael Hornburg<BR>Quartet 1995 8.</H3>
    </CENTER>
    <P>Low life scum, drifting between Portland and New York. I'm told that Portland is quite a nice place, but I suppose the grungeoise have to make the worst of it, where ever they are.</P>
    <P>Some quite nice passages on the isolation of the American wilderness. Neither the sex nor the drugs are particularly memorable, but then these are low life scum . . . . . .wear Converse All Stars, etc - fashion is important throughout and they're inclined to be a bit arty, if of a performance kind that extends to parties and topless gogo - yeah, this is art, art for parties sake. Cute cover.</P>
    <P ALIGN=RIGHT><B>S G Rayment</B></P>
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border2.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <A HREF="http://www.liberator.org.uk/cgi-bin/imagemap/imagemaps/buttons.map"><IMG SRC="../buttons.gif" BORDER=0 USEMAP="#BUTTONS" ISMAP></A>
