<HTML>
  <HEAD>
    <TITLE>Liberator: Issue 235 Reviews</TITLE>
  </HEAD>
  <BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrnd.jpg">
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../read.gif">
      <H1><IMG SRC="../lib_on.gif"><BR>Issue 235 Reviews</H1>
      <BR CLEAR=ALL><HR>
      <H2>Katia Ismailova</H2>
      <H3>(Subtitled, Dir Valeri Todorovski Cert 18)</H3>
    </CENTER>
    <P>Although widely heralded by the mainstream press critics as a classic Russian film noir, I have to confess in being a little disappointed with the final product. Ingeborga Dapkunaite plays the put-upon heroine who is abandoned by an unloving husband more inclined to business than to reinforce his marriage. The poor creature is left to the wiles of her mother-in-law, a novelist, to whom she acts as a typist.</P>
    <P>As the scene moves to the country dacha a local carpenter, a brutish Lawrencian-style artisan takes Katia as a lover. The story's twist revolves around the aftermath of the mother-in- law's timely death. However the revenge motive is not convincingly portrayed in a central performance that is so wooden and expressionless that what could have been is largely a missed opportunity.</P>
    <P>There are better films to see than this.</P>
    <P ALIGN=RIGHT><B>William Tranby</B></P>
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border2.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <A HREF="http://www.liberator.org.uk/cgi-bin/imagemap/imagemaps/buttons.map"><IMG SRC="../buttons.gif" BORDER=0 USEMAP="#BUTTONS" ISMAP></A>
      <map name="BUTTONS">
