<HTML>
  <HEAD>
    <TITLE>Liberator: Issue 235 Reviews</TITLE>
  </HEAD>
  <BODY BACKGROUND="../backgrnd.jpg">
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../read.gif">
      <H1><IMG SRC="../lib_on.gif"><BR>Issue 235 Reviews</H1>
      <BR CLEAR=ALL><HR>
      <H2>Trainspotting</H2>
      <H3>(Dir Danny Boyle Cert 18)</H3>
    </CENTER>
    <P>Following all the hype and the frequent showing of one of the best trailers for some time, this film finally arrived on our screens on 23 February. Was it finally all it was cracked up to be? The simple answer is yes, and then some.</P>
    <P>The film is set in Edinburgh's 1980's drug culture where conventional consumerist values are rejected in favour of the instant hits from heroin shots. The cast of misfits brilliantly led from the front by Ewan McGregor as Renton, subsist in disgusting squats, so graphically portrayed that they create a bizarre twilight world for the viewer that matches the reality experienced by the drug addicts. There are no values, no morality on display here. But remarkably an overarching sense of fun pervades the piece despite its desperate characters and often gruesome action. Black comedy has never been so black.</P>
    <P>Danny Boyle's direction is stylish with a keen sense of the surreal which is at its best when Renton goes in search of drug infused suppositories in the most disgusting toilet in Scotland. To describe what happens on screen next would only spoil the fun.</P>
    <P>When our hero tries an alternative value-free world in London, he becomes an estate agent, which seems rather appropriate under the circumstances. After several relapses back into the drug world we are offered an upbeat ending, which when it is described in all its materialist detail, does not seem that much more enticing than the living hell we have just witnessed for 90 minutes. This is impressive British cinema. See it.</P>
    <P ALIGN=RIGHT><B>William Tranby</B></P>
    <CENTER>
      <IMG SRC="../border2.gif"><BR CLEAR=ALL>
      <A HREF="http://www.liberator.org.uk/cgi-bin/imagemap/imagemaps/buttons.map"><IMG SRC="../buttons.gif" BORDER=0 USEMAP="#BUTTONS" ISMAP></A>
