ation and specie whose	time-scale of existence will be concomitant with that of its own	universe.	</p>		<p>	<li><a href="Essays.html#HBF">The Hilary Factor: Why All		Political Societies Fail</a>	</p>			<p>	It is extraordinary to find all the factors in one person which	will make a volitional society unviable, enabling the author	to summarize the problem and provide points to the answer	in a few pages.	</p>			<p>	<li><a href="Essays.html#CR">How Do You Know You Are Right?</a>	</p>					<p>		One of the most important questions for any		volitional specie.  Finding the answer is critical to the		long term survival of such a specie.		</p>					<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#LTP">Long-Term			Profitability</a>		</p>					<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#LPS">Loopholes and Political			Societies</a>		</p>								<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#PHS">Protest &amp; Human			Survival</a>		</p>					<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#HN">In Certain Cases Terrorism Is			Okay</a>		</p>					<p>		Obviously, I do <b>not</b> ascribe to or believe in		terrorism, but this essays provides some unusual and		important ideas on the subject.		</p>					<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#PROP">		The Concept of Property and the Political State</a>		</p>					<p>		This essays provides an absolute definition of property and		lays the foundation for the subject of <b>ethics</b> which		follows.		</p>					<p>		<li><a href="Essays.html#ETH">Ethics</a>		</p>					<p>		A definitive essay on the subject.  All you need to know on		the subject of ethics.		</p>		</ul></ol><HR NOSHADE><CENTER>[<A HREF="#TOP">Top of Page</A>]</CENTER> <HR NOSHADE><p><B>Contact Information:</b><br></p><p>The<a href="mailto:administrator@freedom-server.co.uk">administrator</a>at The Freedom Server.</p><hr noshade><CENTER><p>&copy; 1995 - The Universal Salvage Corporation</p><p><I>Specialists in Dying Civilizations</I></p></CENTER><HR><p>The URL