ence, and Pedagogy.</B></A><UL><P>Can we teach peace?</P><P>by Stephen G. Barone</P><P>Stephen G. Barone is a practicing psychologist and write who teachesat the University of Wisconsin-Platteville.</P>	<P>		<B>Peace, Political Science, and Pedagogy.</B>	</p>		<p>	<A HREF="Teaching-Peace.txt">Text</A> Format, 11 Kb	file.	</P>		<P>	<A HREF="Teaching-Peace.pdf">Adobe	Acrobat</A> Format, 14 Kb file.	</P></UL><HR><LI> <A NAME="TRIB"><B>The Tribal Premise of Welfare CapitalismIllustrated.</B></A><UL><P>The dangers of "positive entitlement."</P><P>by Anne Wortham</P><P>Dr. Wortham is Associate Professor of Sociology at Illinois StateUniversity and continuing Visiting Scholar, Hoover Institution,Stanford University.</P>	<P>		<B>The Tribal Premise of Welfare Capitalism Illustrated.</B>	</p>	<P>	<A HREF="Tribal-Capitalism.pdf">Adobe	Acrobat</A> Format, 21 Kb file.	</P>		<p>	<A HREF="Tribal-Capitalism.html">HTML</A> Format	</P>	</UL><HR><LI> <A NAME="CANA"><B>Is Canadian Health Care a Good Model for theU.S. to Follow?</B></A><UL><P>Cautions from the Director of the Fraser Institute</P><P>by Michael Walker</P><P>Dr. Walker is Executive Director of the Fraser Institute inVancouver, Canada.</P>		<P>	<B>Is Canadian Health Care a Good Model for the	U.S. to Follow?</B>	</p>		<p>	<A HREF="Canadian-Health-Care.pdf">Adobe	Acrobat</A> Format, 14 Kb file.	</P>		<P>	<A HREF="Canadian-Health-Care.html">HTML</A> Format.	</P></UL><HR><LI> <A NAME="YOU"><B>If You Build It, They Will Come</B></A><UL><P>Medi-Cal built it, advertised it, and they came...in droves.</P><P>by K. L. Billingsley</P><P>K. L. Billingsley is a media fellow of the Pacific Research Institutein San Francisco.</P>	<P>		<B>If You Build It, They Will Come</B>	</p>	<P>	<A HREF="Medi-Cal-Fraud.pdf">Adobe	Acrobat</A> Format, 11 Kb file.	</P>		<p>	<A HREF="Medi-Cal-Fraud.html">HTML</A> Format	